<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 85%; font-weight: bold;"><strong>此横幅蒙谢于令人惊艳的<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mendelssohn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3110636); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3110636&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721523" alt="Mendelssohn" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3110636)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mendelssohn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3110636); return false;">Mendelssohn</a></span>！点击<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/pendleton-miller-s-cognitoseward-collection">此处</a>查看更多他的艺术创作！</strong></span></p>
